subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal began his preparations for Wimbledon with a 6-4, 6-4 victory over the Australian qualifier Matthew Ebden in his opening grass-court match at Queen’s Club on Wednesday in London.
